This approach is more maintainable because:

1. It consolidates multiple lookup methods into a single general-purpose endpoint
2. Uses Zod's refinement to ensure at least one lookup parameter is provided
3. Dynamically constructs the where clause based on provided parameters
4. Makes client usage simpler with a single consistent API

This pattern also scales better if you need to add more ways to find profiles in the future.
